Global Rotary Sprinkler Market Insights
Rotary Sprinkler Market size was valued at USD 2.50 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.80 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Rotary Sprinkler Market Overview
The global rotary sprinkler market is valued at approximately USD 2.5 billion in 2025 and is projected to reach around USD 4.1 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.6% during the forecast period. The market growth is driven by increasing demand for efficient irrigation systems in agriculture, rising awareness about water conservation, and growing adoption of automated systems in various sectors such as residential and commercial landscaping. The rotary sprinkler market is highly competitive, with a mix of established players and emerging companies contributing to the innovation in sprinkler technology.

